# Normalize line endings across platforms. Shell scripts and git hooks MUST be
# LF or they break on POSIX shells; force it so a Windows checkout can't corrupt them.
* text=auto eol=lf

# PowerShell is happy with either; keep the legacy scripts CRLF on Windows checkouts.
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# Binaries (none yet, but future-proof).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
